Subject: Re: [T2] Brakes squeal after 15 mins.

I went through this with metallic pads.
I beveled the edges of the pads, two day cure.
I painted the back of the pads with brake stuff the says eliminates
squeals, $2.00 down the drain.
I cut aluminum shims from beer cans and put them behind the pads, works
good.

Bill M.

